description: Squared is a generative art collection drawn and animated using using P5.js.The rendered code displays a grid of colored pixels that blink in a chaotic, yet calming pattern.Squared is both creatively inspired and technically enabled by OCM Dimensions. A simple example of what can be unlocked by a single inscription. Read about the '10 Dimensions of Ordinals': https://x.com/RabbiGains/status/1675571442635661312 // 1st of its kind reveal: instant, on-chain, random // Each inscription has 100% identical code but renders unique art // Attributes generated using on-chain data during the inscription process // Infinitely scalable to any resolution // Final 12 pieces (#100-#111) are specially curated with 1/1 attributes
name: Squared
